text: Barry Keoghan (; born 18 October 1992) is an Irish actor. He has appeared in the movies Dunkirk, The Killing of a Sacred Deer, for which he won an Irish Film and Television Award for Best Supporting Actor; and Trespass Against Us. In 2022, he had a cameo appearance as The Joker in The Batman. In 2023, he was nominated for an Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor and won a BAFTA Award for Best Actor in a Supporting Role for his role in The Banshees of Inisherin. ==References== Category:BAFTA Award winning actors Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Irish movie actors Category:Irish television actors Category:Irish voice actors Category:Actors from Dublin Category:Actors who played the Joker
